! 2-port synthetic Touchstone v1.1 fixture, DB format
! Same physical network as 2port.s2p: ideal 50-ohm matched 6 dB attenuator.
! S11 = S22 = -infinity dB (perfect match) -- represented as a large
! negative number (-200 dB ~ 1e-10 linear) since true -inf is not standard
! Touchstone. S21 = S12 = -6 dB at 0 deg.
! Z0 = 50 ohm; frequencies in MHz to exercise the unit-dispatch path.
# MHz S DB R 50
1000.0 -200.0 0.0 -6.0 0.0 -6.0 0.0 -200.0 0.0
2000.0 -200.0 0.0 -6.0 0.0 -6.0 0.0 -200.0 0.0
5000.0 -200.0 0.0 -6.0 0.0 -6.0 0.0 -200.0 0.0
10000.0 -200.0 0.0 -6.0 0.0 -6.0 0.0 -200.0 0.0
